WEBVTT

NOTE University of the Air segments and ant communications restaurant sketch

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
[caption on TV] 'UNIVERSITY OF THE AIR'

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:12.000
<v Announcer (Michael Palin)>
[on TV] Hello and welcome to the University of the Air… part seventeen… intraspecific signalling codes in the family formicidea.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.500
<v Chris (Eric Idle)>
That's a stroke of luck, Marcus…

00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:28.000
